data.description: Charming residence located in the Thunderbird Mountain Estates. This delightful 3-bedroom house features two bathrooms, a one-car garage, a cozy wood-burning stove, efficient radiant floor heating, recently upgraded vinyl flooring on the lower level, and generously sized bedrooms. The property sits on half an acre, and an additional 0.59-acre lot adjacent to it is part of the package. The home is embraced by lush trees, adding to its overall appeal. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home today!
